Package: pen.Opt.Gram
Type: Package
Title: Solve penalized regression problems with input being a quadratic form, especially using the Gram matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yuchen Xu
Maintainer: Yuchen Xu <XycXu1015@gmail.com>
Description: Solve different types of penalized regression problems, while the input is in a quadratic form. Especially it has the form of f(A) = 1/2 tr(A G A') - tr(A g) where G is usually X' X / n and g is X' Y / n.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0), Rdpack
Imports: MASS, irlba, Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RSpectra
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RdMacros: Rdpack
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, devtools
VignetteBuilder: knitr
